<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>교환 완료 페이지</title>
</head>
<body>
{{>layouts/header}}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="alert alert-success text-center" role="alert">
        <h4 class="alert-heading">교환 요청이 완료되었습니다!</h4>
        <p>{{message}}</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="mb-0">교환 진행 상황은 '내 거래 내역'에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">메인 페이지로 돌아가기</a>
        <a href="/my-transactions" class="btn btn-secondary">내 거래 내역 보기</a>
    </div>
</div>

{{>layouts/footer}}

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-/JqT3SQfawRcv/BIHPThkBvs0OEvtFFmqPF/lYI/Cxo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>